## FAQs About Pricing Strategy

**What is a pricing strategy and why does it matter?**  
Itâ€™s the framework you use to set and adjust pricesâ€”based on value, customers, and business goalsâ€”not just cost.  

**How do I choose the right model for my business?**  
Assess your value proposition, market position, customer segments, capacity to deliver, and long-term goals. Then test and refine.  

**What mistakes should I avoid?**  
Avoid pricing purely on cost, competing solely on price, ignoring customer value, failing to update pricing, and not segmenting your offer.  

